{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the future, humanity embarks on a project to terraform distant planets and make them habitable. You are a member of the team of specialists in greening and ecosystem adaptation. Your task is to find rare plants, clean up the environment, and prepare it for vegetation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The planet you have arrived on is harsh and inhospitable. You will gather local flora samples and use them to turn this barren wasteland into a green oasis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exploration of Uncharted Territories</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into vast locations, explore rocky wastelands, and find rare plant specimens crucial for greening the planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collection and Cleansing</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather as many plant samples as possible, cleanse the areas from pollutants, and prepare them for subsequent greening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Terraforming Technologies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use advanced technologies to adapt and cultivate plants, transforming barren lands into flourishing gardens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you turn a lifeless planet into a green paradise?</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Point of interest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3125700/f3d1e6129a702ac21357e8a41845f353c611f73b.jpg"},{"name":"Daily fitness","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3125700/f8b4b817bc0c635a78647f66c323d3d3434c1bb7.jpg"},{"name":"Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3125700/97289b1f18d367789d095bfa6f290cdcc5f71272.jpg"},{"name":"Botanist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.